<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10603337>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2–10. New records for Oaxaca: 2) Erichsonia dentifrons Westwood, 1849; 3) Scatopyrodes iris (Bates, 1884); 4) Strangalia veracruzana Hovore & Chemsak, 2005; 5) Arhopalus asperatus (LeConte, 1859); 6) Arhopalus obsoletus (Randall, 1838); 7) Chlorida cincta Guérin-Méneville, 1844; 8) Callichroma holochlorum holochlorum Bates, 1872; 9) Dexithea klugii (Laporte & Gory, 1836); 10) Xylotrechus sagittatus chiricahuae Chemsak, 1959." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10603337/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

